1
00:00:27,210 --> 00:00:29,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE CASEBOOK OF ARNE</font>

2
00:01:47,290 --> 00:01:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}PART 9: NOT ALL THAT GLITTERS IS GOLD</font>

3
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:02,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you even read quietly,
 Lynn Reinweiß?</font>

4
00:02:05,090 --> 00:02:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back again, kiddo.</font>

5
00:02:07,590 --> 00:02:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've brought you another client 
today, kiddo. See?</font>

6
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:16,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then, um, Mrs. Sheila,</font>

7
00:02:16,890 --> 00:02:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would you mind telling us your request?</font>

8
00:02:21,150 --> 00:02:22,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Certainly.</font>

9
00:02:22,590 --> 00:02:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is very embarrassing for me,</font>

10
00:02:25,330 --> 00:02:28,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'd like you to find out 
if my husband's been unfaithful.</font>

11
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he's been unfaithful?</font>

12
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two months ago,</font>

13
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:38,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">my husband fell down a staircase 
and was severely injured.</font>

14
00:02:39,340 --> 00:02:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Due to his injuries, 
he lost the ability to speak.</font>

15
00:02:44,370 --> 00:02:48,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Up to that point, my husband 
had been a very kind person,</font>

16
00:02:49,260 --> 00:02:51,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but after his release
 from the hospital,</font>

17
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it was like he was a different person.
A very distant one.</font>

18
00:02:56,070 --> 00:03:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. And that's why 
you suspect him of cheating?</font>

19
00:03:00,380 --> 00:03:01,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

20
00:03:01,270 --> 00:03:02,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How stupid.</font>

21
00:03:02,220 --> 00:03:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne!</font>

22
00:03:03,790 --> 00:03:07,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I agree. 
I think it is quite foolish myself.</font>

23
00:03:08,710 --> 00:03:13,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But as my husband is invisible, 
him being unable to speak makes things...</font>

24
00:03:13,580 --> 00:03:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">J-Just a moment. Did you say "invisible"?</font>

25
00:03:17,290 --> 00:03:19,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I suppose I forgot
 to mention that part.</font>

26
00:03:20,220 --> 00:03:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While I am a normal human, 
my husband is an invisible man.</font>

27
00:03:24,850 --> 00:03:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE CASE OF THE INVISIBLE MAN'S FALL</font>

28
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}An in-vi-si-ble man?</font>

29
00:03:28,670 --> 00:03:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

30
00:03:33,050 --> 00:03:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good afternoon.</font>

31
00:03:34,830 --> 00:03:38,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for coming. Please come in.</font>

32
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne, hurry up.</font>

33
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:50,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then, I will take my leave.</font>

34
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have brought our guests.</font>

35
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:59,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come in.</font>

36
00:04:02,930 --> 00:04:05,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incredible.</font>

37
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:08,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They really <i>are</i> invisible.</font>

38
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's almost like an optical illusion.</font>

39
00:04:10,980 --> 00:04:13,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm my husband's second wife.</font>

40
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:17,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His first wife, who was 
also invisible, passed away,</font>

41
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:20,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but they had three sons together.</font>

42
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:24,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have a very good relationship
 with them, however.</font>

43
00:04:25,420 --> 00:04:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

44
00:04:27,250 --> 00:04:29,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does the father get along with his sons?</font>

45
00:04:29,590 --> 00:04:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before the accident, 
they didn't see eye to eye at all.</font>

46
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:38,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But since the accident, he's been letting
 his sons help with the business,</font>

47
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:43,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and when he needs to go out,
 one of them accompanies him,</font>

48
00:04:43,710 --> 00:04:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so he's come to depend
 on them much more.</font>

49
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:53,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As it happens, I was out of the house
on the day of the accident.</font>

50
00:04:53,890 --> 00:04:58,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the time I returned, the boys had 
already taken my husband to the hospital.</font>

51
00:04:59,020 --> 00:05:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't allowed to visit him there.</font>

52
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:06,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when he was released, it was like 
he was a completely different person.</font>

53
00:05:07,860 --> 00:05:10,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. We'll take the case.</font>

54
00:05:11,770 --> 00:05:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean it?</font>

55
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. But not to look into any infidelity.</font>

56
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll investigate the accident.</font>

57
00:05:19,780 --> 00:05:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my husband.</font>

58
00:05:23,490 --> 00:05:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are his eldest and middle sons.</font>

59
00:05:25,980 --> 00:05:27,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This gentleman is, um, Ar—</font>

60
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:31,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arne Neuntöte. I'm a private detective.</font>

61
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm his assistant, Lynn.</font>

62
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this is Amy.</font>

63
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Detective?</font>

64
00:05:47,300 --> 00:05:50,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forgive me. I accidentally
 squeezed too hard.</font>

65
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? To what do we owe the pleasure,
 Mister Detective?</font>

66
00:05:55,980 --> 00:06:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. I'm going to start looking 
into your father's accident.</font>

67
00:06:07,700 --> 00:06:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. However, it was 
undeniably an accident.</font>

68
00:06:10,970 --> 00:06:13,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing about it warrants an investi—</font>

69
00:06:13,390 --> 00:06:16,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure. But this is my job.</font>

70
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:19,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unless you're trying to hide something,
I'd welcome your cooperation.</font>

71
00:06:22,230 --> 00:06:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, I heard there were 
<i>three</i> brothers living in this manor.</font>

72
00:06:26,430 --> 00:06:29,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. The youngest is out of 
the house at the moment.</font>

73
00:06:29,530 --> 00:06:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

74
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:33,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, I'd like to inspect 
the manor right away.</font>

75
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:35,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show me around.</font>

76
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Just who do you think...</font>

77
00:06:40,570 --> 00:06:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it easy. I'm not trying 
to accuse you of anything.</font>

78
00:06:45,050 --> 00:06:47,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm merely interested in the truth.</font>

79
00:06:47,260 --> 00:06:48,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

80
00:06:52,970 --> 00:06:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay, Dad?</font>

81
00:06:55,340 --> 00:06:58,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He must be tired. Why don't 
you take him to his room?</font>

82
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:03,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I shall show you around.</font>

83
00:07:04,230 --> 00:07:06,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the staircase in question.</font>

84
00:07:06,530 --> 00:07:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The three of us heard a loud noise and 
a scream, and when we ran here to look,</font>

85
00:07:10,990 --> 00:07:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we found our father down there, bleeding.</font>

86
00:07:15,100 --> 00:07:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you use this staircase often?</font>

87
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father and Sheila do.</font>

88
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our three rooms are rather further away.</font>

89
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

90
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? Are you satisfied now?</font>

91
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not even close. I want to 
interview you each separately.</font>

92
00:07:29,790 --> 00:07:32,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">F-Fine.</font>

93
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:37,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what did you want to ask about?</font>

94
00:07:37,150 --> 00:07:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First of all, the time of the accident.</font>

95
00:07:39,740 --> 00:07:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it true you brothers were 
the only other people in the house?</font>

96
00:07:43,670 --> 00:07:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. My middle brother and I were 
playing chess in another room.</font>

97
00:07:47,850 --> 00:07:50,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The youngest said 
he was drinking in the kitchen.</font>

98
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

99
00:07:52,450 --> 00:07:55,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, do you bear a grudge 
against your father for any reason?</font>

100
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that supposed to mean?</font>

101
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just getting the facts straight.</font>

102
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I do not.</font>

103
00:08:04,100 --> 00:08:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If any of us do, 
it would be my middle brother.</font>

104
00:08:08,620 --> 00:08:11,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm ashamed to say this, but, well...</font>

105
00:08:12,530 --> 00:08:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems he's had feelings for Sheila.</font>

106
00:08:17,820 --> 00:08:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? What do you want?</font>

107
00:08:20,990 --> 00:08:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm afraid I don't have a lot of time, 
so try to keep it brief.</font>

108
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, I'll cut to the chase.</font>

109
00:08:26,690 --> 00:08:29,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you desire your mother-in-law?</font>

110
00:08:29,530 --> 00:08:30,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

111
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:33,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Lord Arne! How could you 
<i>ask</i> something like that?!</font>

112
00:08:33,900 --> 00:08:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I was trying to keep it brief.</font>

113
00:08:36,110 --> 00:08:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, that may be, but even so!</font>

114
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That is to say, that's not the issue.</font>

115
00:08:41,250 --> 00:08:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Couldn't you phrase it
 a little differently? I mean—</font>

116
00:08:44,290 --> 00:08:45,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ahem.</font>

117
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a load of garbage. 
What a sickening thing to suggest.</font>

118
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you don't?</font>

119
00:08:50,180 --> 00:08:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bet I don't.</font>

120
00:08:52,030 --> 00:08:55,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did go out together a few times,
just the two of us,</font>

121
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:58,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but that's only because 
I was sizing her up.</font>

122
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meaning?</font>

123
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:04,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm convinced that woman latched on
to my father for his money.</font>

124
00:09:04,230 --> 00:09:05,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Huh?</font>

125
00:09:06,190 --> 00:09:10,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But of course, she never let 
her guard down around me.</font>

126
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:16,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As soon as my father decided to remarry,
 I started looking into her background.</font>

127
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:19,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She comes from a family
 of failed aristocrats,</font>

128
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:23,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and was once married to someone in 
another country, if only for a few months.</font>

129
00:09:24,010 --> 00:09:26,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She wed a very wealthy man
who was almost 80,</font>

130
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and it sounds like he had
 a fatal accident soon after.</font>

131
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A fatal accident?</font>

132
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:34,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, he fell down a flight 
of stairs and hit his head.</font>

133
00:09:34,990 --> 00:09:37,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like what happened here.</font>

134
00:09:39,570 --> 00:09:42,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what a fool my father was.</font>

135
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:46,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The moment my mother dies, 
he hooks up with this shady broad.</font>

136
00:09:50,270 --> 00:09:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems you investigated her
 quite thoroughly.</font>

137
00:09:54,570 --> 00:09:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-A-Anyway, if you insist on 
strutting about like you're the police,</font>

138
00:09:57,880 --> 00:10:00,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">can't you at least 
employ a lighter touch?</font>

139
00:10:00,070 --> 00:10:04,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, even my little brother 
has problems with our father.</font>

140
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:08,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He gambled away a fortune, then when 
he tried to get Father to shoulder his debts,</font>

141
00:10:08,830 --> 00:10:11,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father got so mad,
 he nearly disowned him.</font>

142
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good afternoon!</font>

143
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:30,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the youngest brother.</font>

144
00:10:30,500 --> 00:10:31,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey there.</font>

145
00:10:32,210 --> 00:10:33,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Arne Neuntöte.</font>

146
00:10:41,370 --> 00:10:42,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

147
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-This way, please.</font>

148
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:48,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that ring!</font>

149
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

150
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:50,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've seen it before!</font>

151
00:10:50,950 --> 00:10:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's from the latest 
Amelia Wilson collection!</font>

152
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:55,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

153
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:58,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's gorgeous! It looks so pretty on you!</font>

154
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tch. Got yourself all dolled up, huh?</font>

155
00:11:05,510 --> 00:11:09,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speaking of, some of Mother's jewelry 
has gone missing bit by bit lately,</font>

156
00:11:09,740 --> 00:11:12,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while your collection's 
been growing bit by bit.</font>

157
00:11:12,390 --> 00:11:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

158
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:16,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you trying to say?</font>

159
00:11:20,810 --> 00:11:23,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So today is my turn, huh?</font>

160
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cool. Ask whatever you want.</font>

161
00:11:25,750 --> 00:11:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it true you got your father
 to shoulder your debts?</font>

162
00:11:29,420 --> 00:11:30,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep, sure is.</font>

163
00:11:30,700 --> 00:11:34,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I got brutally chewed out and 
was almost kicked out of the house.</font>

164
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you resent him for that?</font>

165
00:11:36,450 --> 00:11:38,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that what 
a rebellious phase is all about?</font>

166
00:11:38,990 --> 00:11:43,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh. Next question. 
It's about what you just said.</font>

167
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you mean my mother's jewelry?</font>

168
00:11:46,020 --> 00:11:47,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it's the truth.</font>

169
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After that debt thing with my dad, 
he completely cut off my allowance,</font>

170
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:54,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I sniffed out pretty much 
all of the valuables in this house.</font>

171
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell my brothers, okay?</font>

172
00:11:57,400 --> 00:12:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But even I wouldn't think of selling off
 Mom's keepsakes like that.</font>

173
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

174
00:12:04,410 --> 00:12:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you seen your brothers or mother-in-law
 with any unusual items recently?</font>

175
00:12:08,670 --> 00:12:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unusual items?</font>

176
00:12:11,590 --> 00:12:12,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that you mention it,</font>

177
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found a pretty unusual pocket watch 
in Sheila's room the other day.</font>

178
00:12:16,590 --> 00:12:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It had all sorts of jewels 
stuck to the front.</font>

179
00:12:19,810 --> 00:12:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looked pretty darn pricey.</font>

180
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad never carries a watch,</font>

181
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm betting it was a gift
 from some other man.</font>

182
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:30,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, that woman really turns my stomach.</font>

183
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But y'know, my older brother's the one 
who's had the most trouble with Dad.</font>

184
00:12:36,230 --> 00:12:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He bombed at business, and Dad said, 
"I'm not leaving the estate to your type."</font>

185
00:12:40,820 --> 00:12:42,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He hasn't been able to let that go.</font>

186
00:12:43,150 --> 00:12:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

187
00:13:03,890 --> 00:13:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what—</font>

188
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that...</font>

189
00:13:10,980 --> 00:13:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne, a-are they cheating? 
Are we catching them in the act?</font>

190
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Settle down.</font>

191
00:13:16,310 --> 00:13:18,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe he's giving her a present.</font>

192
00:13:18,050 --> 00:13:20,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seems pretty by the book.</font>

193
00:13:23,780 --> 00:13:26,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't this something 
we should be investigating?</font>

194
00:13:26,350 --> 00:13:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knock yourself out.</font>

195
00:13:29,860 --> 00:13:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me, please!</font>

196
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:34,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I help you?</font>

197
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:39,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, there is something 
I would like to ask you.</font>

198
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes?</font>

199
00:13:41,980 --> 00:13:43,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I beg your pardon.</font>

200
00:13:43,950 --> 00:13:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a famous private detective...</font>

201
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...'s assistant. 
My name is Lynn Reinweiß.</font>

202
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-A detective?</font>

203
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:55,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the question I'd like to ask is:
Are you and Mrs. Sheila...</font>

204
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in some kind of intimate relationship?</font>

205
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:02,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Myself and Madam Sheila?</font>

206
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:05,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no. Nothing of the sort.</font>

207
00:14:05,890 --> 00:14:09,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Th-Then, why were you meeting just now?</font>

208
00:14:09,530 --> 00:14:11,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, so you saw us.</font>

209
00:14:12,460 --> 00:14:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was delivering an item she'd ordered.</font>

210
00:14:15,750 --> 00:14:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An item she'd ordered?</font>

211
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. She has been asking me to find 
a medicine to help her husband.</font>

212
00:14:24,870 --> 00:14:28,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, s-so that's why.</font>

213
00:14:28,960 --> 00:14:32,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She is such a faithful wife.</font>

214
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:34,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does she often order things from you?</font>

215
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:35,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

216
00:14:35,970 --> 00:14:40,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, yes. Perhaps once or twice a month.</font>

217
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:43,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After I finish my business
 with her husband.</font>

218
00:14:43,280 --> 00:14:45,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What sorts of things does she order?</font>

219
00:14:45,110 --> 00:14:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, let's see. I specialize 
in everyday household goods,</font>

220
00:14:49,210 --> 00:14:51,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and she often orders 
tea leaves and perfume.</font>

221
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also tableware, candles, weed killer.</font>

222
00:14:55,290 --> 00:14:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's also ordered oil 
for lubricating door joints before.</font>

223
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:03,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose she cares 
for the furniture by herself.</font>

224
00:15:03,070 --> 00:15:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She truly is a dutiful wife.</font>

225
00:15:10,920 --> 00:15:15,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must apologize. They should 
be done with business soon.</font>

226
00:15:15,260 --> 00:15:19,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter. We only came to see 
if the middle brother was out of the house.</font>

227
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

228
00:15:20,170 --> 00:15:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, uh, I believe he is out
 at the moment.</font>

229
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:25,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

230
00:15:31,420 --> 00:15:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So how is the investigation going?</font>

231
00:15:35,650 --> 00:15:39,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, pardon me. This seems to be damaged.</font>

232
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you going to fix it?</font>

233
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:43,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not handy enough for that.</font>

234
00:15:44,140 --> 00:15:46,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll have to get someone to repair it.</font>

235
00:15:55,100 --> 00:15:56,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this picture from?</font>

236
00:15:56,490 --> 00:16:01,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, uh, that's me and a patient 
from a hospital I used to work at.</font>

237
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:07,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to the agency tomorrow. 
I'll share my conclusions then.</font>

238
00:16:07,070 --> 00:16:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

239
00:16:09,090 --> 00:16:10,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-All right.</font>

240
00:16:11,820 --> 00:16:14,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please tell me, Lord Arne.</font>

241
00:16:14,490 --> 00:16:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What have you concluded? 
What did you find out?</font>

242
00:16:18,210 --> 00:16:21,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not figure it out yourself for once?</font>

243
00:16:21,330 --> 00:16:22,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss "Famous Detective."</font>

244
00:16:26,340 --> 00:16:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of the sons hold grudges
 against their father.</font>

245
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:34,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it probably wasn't 
an accident after all, right?</font>

246
00:16:36,260 --> 00:16:39,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, there's something about Mrs. Sheila.</font>

247
00:16:39,260 --> 00:16:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They might have gotten
 ahead of me this time.</font>

248
00:16:42,860 --> 00:16:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Did you say something?</font>

249
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

250
00:16:49,440 --> 00:16:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And also, Lord Arne, why don't 
you talk to the husband directly?</font>

251
00:16:54,570 --> 00:16:56,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if he can't speak, 
he can still write—</font>

252
00:16:56,590 --> 00:16:58,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would serve no purpose.</font>

253
00:16:58,300 --> 00:17:01,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Serve no purpose?</font>

254
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:30,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the last three days, I've been 
observing the brothers' movements.</font>

255
00:17:31,190 --> 00:17:34,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been observing them?</font>

256
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:37,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am able to manipulate my own blood.</font>

257
00:17:39,330 --> 00:17:41,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I left some of my blood on each of them</font>

258
00:17:42,210 --> 00:17:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so that I could see which rooms 
they slept in each night.</font>

259
00:17:46,460 --> 00:17:47,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I've concluded...</font>

260
00:17:49,560 --> 00:17:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the three of them were taking turns 
sleeping in your husband's bedroom.</font>

261
00:17:55,350 --> 00:17:56,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

262
00:17:56,680 --> 00:18:02,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The three brothers have conspired to make it
 look like your husband is still alive.</font>

263
00:18:02,970 --> 00:18:05,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Then, my husband is...</font>

264
00:18:05,470 --> 00:18:09,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The day of the so-called accident, 
the three of them likely murdered him.</font>

265
00:18:11,990 --> 00:18:15,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One corner of the garden smells
very strongly of blood.</font>

266
00:18:16,760 --> 00:18:18,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suspect that's where the body is.</font>

267
00:18:18,610 --> 00:18:20,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

268
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:24,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seemed like a man's body 
that had been dead for a month or two.</font>

269
00:18:25,100 --> 00:18:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mrs. Sheila?</font>

270
00:18:27,270 --> 00:18:29,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The investigation is over.</font>

271
00:18:29,140 --> 00:18:30,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can go home now.</font>

272
00:18:30,320 --> 00:18:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Lord Arne!</font>

273
00:18:32,440 --> 00:18:36,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't send her home 
when the killers are still there!</font>

274
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A detective's job is merely
 to solve the case.</font>

275
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:41,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, yes, but still...</font>

276
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't just send our client to her death.</font>

277
00:18:46,980 --> 00:18:50,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine. I'll let you stay here for one night.</font>

278
00:18:50,150 --> 00:18:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you need something after that,
 get in touch with Sheeeep.</font>

279
00:18:53,180 --> 00:18:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne.</font>

280
00:18:55,600 --> 00:19:00,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're willing to give up 
and abandon it all, that is.</font>

281
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

282
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you really think it's safe
 for us to go there?</font>

283
00:19:25,840 --> 00:19:30,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I must apologize for unintentionally 
giving you the wrong impression</font>

284
00:19:30,310 --> 00:19:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">during your investigation the other day."</font>

285
00:19:32,390 --> 00:19:37,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"To clear up any misunderstanding, 
I ask you to visit the manor again."</font>

286
00:19:37,110 --> 00:19:40,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The entire family looks forward
 to seeing you."</font>

287
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to worry.</font>

288
00:19:42,610 --> 00:19:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zwei and I will be right there with you.</font>

289
00:19:44,910 --> 00:19:46,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I guess you're right.</font>

290
00:19:47,340 --> 00:19:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I do want to check in on Mrs. Sheila.</font>

291
00:19:54,040 --> 00:19:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Is something the matter?</font>

292
00:19:57,280 --> 00:20:02,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know what, Lynn? We can't just 
show up empty-handed now, can we?</font>

293
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:02,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

294
00:20:02,630 --> 00:20:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go and buy them 
some sweets or something.</font>

295
00:20:05,550 --> 00:20:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, w-w-wait just a second. Wh-What?</font>

296
00:20:13,870 --> 00:20:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, there you are. 
We've been expecting you.</font>

297
00:20:16,450 --> 00:20:18,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it just you today?</font>

298
00:20:18,350 --> 00:20:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That should be obvious.</font>

299
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, of course.</font>

300
00:20:22,800 --> 00:20:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, please come in.</font>

301
00:20:25,070 --> 00:20:29,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheila informed us that 
we may have inadvertently led you</font>

302
00:20:29,350 --> 00:20:32,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to a very unfortunate 
misunderstanding of the situation.</font>

303
00:20:32,230 --> 00:20:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is your mother-in-law now?</font>

304
00:20:34,390 --> 00:20:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must apologize. She just went out.</font>

305
00:20:38,940 --> 00:20:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She did, huh?</font>

306
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:45,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you see this, you'll understand 
once and for all that we're all innocent.</font>

307
00:20:45,840 --> 00:20:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father, we're coming in.</font>

308
00:20:55,990 --> 00:21:00,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems you were under the impression
 my father had died, but as you can see,</font>

309
00:21:01,900 --> 00:21:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father is right here with us.</font>

310
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:36,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: MICHAEL ARNOLD</font>

311
00:21:36,030 --> 00:21:40,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TIMING: HENRY LIN
EDITING: SMR</font>

312
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}QUALITY CONTROL: ELISABETH CRIST
TRANSLATION CHECK: ELIZABETH ELLIS</font>

